SYNOPSIS

    In dist.ini:

     [AddFile::FromFS]
     src=/home/ujang/doc/tips.txt
     dest=share/tips.txt

    To add more files:

     [AddFile::FromFS / OtherTips]
     src=/home/ujang/doc/othertips.txt
     dest=share/othertips.txt

DESCRIPTION

    This plugin lets you add single file(s) from local filesystem to your
    build.

SEE ALSO

    Dist::Zilla::Plugin::GatherDir is the standard way to add files to your
    build, but this plugin currently does not offer a way to include single
    files. Wishlist ticket already created:
    https://rt.cpan.org/Ticket/Display.html?id=105583

    Dist::Zilla::Plugin::GenerateFile

    Dist::Zilla::Plugin::AddFile::FromCode

    Dist::Zilla::Plugin::AddFile::FromCommand

